# 11. Camera smoothing

Readable version:

```js
function updateCamera() {
  camera.x += (cameraTarget.x - camera.x) * config.theta;
  camera.y += (cameraTarget.y - camera.y) * config.theta;
  camera.zoom += (cameraTarget.zoom - camera.zoom) * config.theta;
}
```

---

# 12. Main loop

Readable version:

```js
function tickFrame() {
  updatePhysics();
  updateStreams();
  updateCamera();

  if (tick % 3 === 0) {
    spawnStreamParticle();
  }

  tick++;
}

setInterval(tickFrame, 10);
```

So it updates every 10 ms, i.e. about 100 times per second.

